snippet.title: Meme Mayhem trailer
snippet.description:
Do your roguelite games not have enough memes? Want to fight your social media enemies in nailbiting emoji battles? Log in to the world of Super Media Hero. Scroll the in-game feed, react to posts, and pick fights with celebrities. Slide into the DMs of characters like Strong Doge, Elton Mars, and Sad Toad. Whether you're a selfless idealist or just looking for fortune and fame, you're on your way to the top of the social media food chain.

Please wishlist our game and play the demo on Steam.
